OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FOften cloudy with a few
OL,6,Fbrighter or sunny spells but also
OL,7,Foccasional showers. Any wintriness is
OL,8,Flikely to become restricted to highest
OL,9,Fhills. Feeling chilly, despite easing
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FFine
OL,13,FSaturday, with brighter or sunny
OL,14,Fspells, light winds, and isolated
OL,15,Fshowers. Rain spreading east Sunday,
OL,16,Fthen colder again with showers
OL,17,Ffollowing, wintry over hills. Breezy,
OL,18,Fbut mostly dry Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
